TRAINING SCRIPT FOR TOEFL INDEPENDENT WRITING

Ugly bash script that scores essay-writing abilities using GPT-3.

High-level description:
1. Generates a topic for an essay using the OpenAI API;
2. Opens a text file in the vim editor for the user to write an essay on the generated topic;
3. Scores the essay and provides recommendations for improvement using the OpenAI API;
4. Adds the score and recommendations to the text file.
